INSERT INTO leads (userId, companyName, website, industry, companySize, location, score, status, notes, createdAt, updatedAt)
SELECT 
  u.id,
  'TechHealth Solutions',
  'https://techhealthsolutions.example.com',
  'Healthcare Technology',
  '100-500',
  'San Francisco, CA',
  85,
  'new',
  'High-growth healthcare tech company with strong funding',
  NOW(),
  NOW()
FROM users u
WHERE u.openId = (SELECT OWNER_OPEN_ID FROM (SELECT 'OWNER_OPEN_ID' as OWNER_OPEN_ID) as tmp)
LIMIT 1;
